cluster-architecture.help:
Manages buildout of cluster architecture on AWS.

Kubernetes clusters are launched using EKS.

In addition a system layer is provisioned for each cluster.
cluster-architecture.name: cluster-architecture

container-architecture.help:
Manages buildout of container architecture on AWS.

All containers not launched in an EKS cluster are launched in ECS and managed in this repository:

* ECS clusters
* ECS services
* ECS tasks
container-architecture.name: container-architecture

database-architecture.help:
Manages buildout of database architecture on AWS and MongoDB Atlas:

AWS:
* RDS database clusters
* Elasticache Redis clusters
* OpenSearch clusters

MongoDB Atlas
* Projects
* Clusters
* AWS peering
database-architecture.name: database-architecture

dns-architecture.help:
Manages buildout of DNS architecture on AWS:

* Certificates
* Route53 Zones

As well as providing a way to provision Route53 records for individual domains.

Redirects within a domain are also provisioned here.
dns-architecture.name: dns-architecture

flyio-architecture.help: Manages buildout of FlyIO apps and secrets
flyio-architecture.name: flyio-architecture

snowflake-architecture.help:
Manages Snowflake architecture:

* Roles
* Monitoring integration with Datadog
* Storage integration with S3
snowflake-architecture.name: snowflake-architecture

storage-architecture.help:
Manages buildout of storage architecture on AWS:

* EFS filesystems
* S3 buckets
* Access log S3 buckets

Also manages buildout of legacy storage architecture predating the organization account setup.
storage-architecture.name: storage-architecture

terraform-aws-architecture.help:
Coordinates all the assets from architecture repositories that buildout on AWS.

Additionally handles sharing of assets between AWS accounts.
terraform-aws-architecture.name: terraform-aws-architecture

terraform-aws-networking.help:
Manages networking on AWS:

* Account networking
* Account peering
* Client VPN
terraform-aws-networking.name: terraform-aws-networking

terraform-aws-secretsmanager.help: Coordinates all secrets between AWS accounts
terraform-aws-secretsmanager.name: terraform-aws-secretsmanager
